com.mysema.query
Interface Projectable

All Known Subinterfaces:
ColQuery, HQLQuery, JDOQLQuery
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractColQuery, AbstractHQLQuery, AbstractJDOQLQuery, AbstractJPAQLQuery, AbstractSQLQuery, ColQueryImpl, CustomQueryable, HQLQueryBase, HQLQueryImpl, JDOQLQueryImpl, JPAQLQueryImpl, OracleQuery, ProjectableAdapter, QueryBaseWithProjection, SQLQuery
public interface Projectable

Projectable defines default projection methods for Query implementations. All Querydsl query implementations should implement this interface.

Version:
$Id$
Author:
tiwe
